{"tid":2321733,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"HASecret 又爆料：女皇醫院高層對富豪病人有優待","createTime":"2020-12-11T17:45:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T00:51:55.000Z","uid":5195,"like":42,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1f211ec8e4cb824e44e0ebb6b1c3944291dfe02d","tid":2321733,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:45:36.000Z","msg":"#11287<br />\n&quot;今次第四波，跳舞群組有很多都是達官貴人，大部份是入公立醫院接受治療。<br />\n達官貴人在公立醫院的行為，就是好像在茶餐廳 點五星酒店的餐。在九龍女皇醫院近日有一件非常過分安排。<br />\n<br />\n一位富豪，家中有多名成員相繼中招，但家中年長成員因為身體不適被安排入院治療，入院就被護士發現家中有多名成員中招，因為這位長者是與多名確人士有緊密接觸，所以便安排到隔離病房繼續接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n病人在家一直都有陪人照顧，富豪堅持要陪人一直陪伴病人，無論病人是否安排到隔離病房，並聲稱如果未能安排便會開記招，最終女皇醫院高層安排是:<br />\n陪人**突然**身體不適，醫生便安排clinical adm 到隔離病房接受治療，並安排病人及其陪人到同一病房，同一房間。<br />\n<br />\n問題就岀來了，兩個懷疑個案，如果其中一個確診，同住同一房間的病人便會被傳染。<br />\n就是因為這個原因，陪人就簽了同意書，同意自己要付上被傳染的責任。<br />\n<br />\n為何女皇醫院對此富豪有如此優待？<br />\n一直覺得香港醫療還是有水準，不會因為任何人的背景有什麼優待。<br />\n<br />\n今次事件完全是對權貴跪低的完美示範。<br />\n<br />\n女皇醫院高層們難辭其咎，能否給我們香港人一個合理解釋。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/731331330322257/posts/3494068370715192/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F731331330322257%2Fposts%2F3494068370715192%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmjYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=1815df8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/731331330322257/posts/3494068370715192/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a><br />\n張竹君，出黎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad67c687261f99c998f7333d90dda01d5ec6b9a","tid":2321733,"uid":91771,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:52:23.000Z","msg":"HA 應該係Dr Yu同Dr Ho兩條淫婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"291623b738e52d19f063ab6007dda097a7ad2ac2","tid":2321733,"uid":384990,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:55:08.000Z","msg":"其實好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a82592a33299acb9e1a9536496bc905db4c90f","tid":2321733,"uid":7076,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T18:14:59.000Z","msg":"不嬲香港有錢有權=可以打橫嚟行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醫生嘅建議都可以 WFC <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751332acad2a341ec524ba17ccf7bf0e2562ca31","tid":2321733,"uid":25468,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T18:18:18.000Z","msg":"其實不嬲都係咁，啲有錢佬係好撚麻煩"},{"pid":"dab87f33a7348c67371e8d7a9fd43e3fcdb7de49","tid":2321733,"uid":201604,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T18:18:25.000Z","msg":"你咁有錢 畀錢叫啲武肺病毒唔好感染你咪得囉"},{"pid":"524aa245f716551e093c1592bd77d6ef6244435e","tid":2321733,"uid":25468,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T18:19:09.000Z","msg":"如果私家可以醫武肺，班富豪會一早轉晒院"},{"pid":"4876bf9b62abbdb75fe9a62ac33855c201bba592","tid":2321733,"uid":49336,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T18:20:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce13314fdaecef54b275a6e3fef38eca3aece8c0","tid":2321733,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"751332acad2a341ec524ba17ccf7bf0e2562ca31","tid":2321733,"uid":25468,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T18:18:18.000Z","msg":"其實不嬲都係咁，啲有錢佬係好撚麻煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T18:20:55.000Z","msg":"有兩個臭錢就咩道德法律都唔講<br />\n為富不仁就係呢D"},{"pid":"f746cdf663c966f66fdda0cf461d75dc486d4e99","tid":2321733,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T18:23:34.000Z","msg":"因為山頂醫院唔收囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebdc3015d74c915c8a097fcb79420dee561f73e3","tid":2321733,"uid":131918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T18:27:22.000Z","msg":"高層驚乜<br 